194
00:11:29.290 --> 00:11:30.458
<i>o incluso las Carolinas,</i>

195
00:11:30.541 --> 00:11:32.042
<i>el amo te amenazaba:</i>

196
00:11:32.793 --> 00:11:35.838
<i>"Si no te portas bien,</i>
