299
00:17:44.581 --> 00:17:47.000
<i>Nos seguía a Willie y a mí.</i>

300
00:17:49.586 --> 00:17:52.131
<i>Y siempre que nos parábamos a descansar</i>

301
00:17:52.214 --> 00:17:55.759
